Package: sigstart
Title: Parse Mutation Files to Formats Compatible with Signature Analysis Toolkits
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "El-Kamand", , "selkamand@ccia.org.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2270-8088"))
Description: Parse small variants, copy number changes, and structural rearrangements from commmon bioinformatics file formats like VCFs and  segment files. 
  Convert these data into formats compatible with signature analysis toolkits.
